Kasneb has announced an extension of the deadline for booking the April examinations. The deadline for the booking of the April examination had been scheduled for February 28 but has now been pushed to March 4. The April Examination will be administered from Monday, April 4 to Wednesday, April 6. The associate in procurement and supplies of Kenya (APS-K) examination period will however extend to April 7. The examination will be administered on a computer-based platform.